1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Did you know training a single LLM can emit as much carbon as five cars over their entire lifetimes?

2
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:15,000
Meet EcoCompute AI, the first "Green AI" Architect powered by Gemini 3 Pro.

3
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:23,000
It’s not just a linter. It’s a virtual Performance Engineer that sees your architecture—literally.

4
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:31,000
You can paste your PyTorch code or even upload a hand-drawn sketch of your neural network.

5
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:40,000
Gemini 3 analyzes the visual topology to detect hidden bottlenecks that static analysis might miss.

6
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:49,000
But we don't just guess. EcoCompute uses Gemini's Agentic capabilities to ground every decision.

7
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:59,000
Watch as it uses Google Search to pull real-time 2026 hardware specs, like the latest NVIDIA B200 TDPs.

8
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:10,000
Then, it uses the Code Execution tool to write and run Python scripts in a sandbox, verifying Arithmetic Intensity math.

9
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:19,000
The result? A comprehensive "Deep Energy Audit" with a structured breakdown of Joules and Carbon.

10
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:28,000
Check out the "Decision Triangle." It forces you to balance Performance, Cost, and Carbon Efficiency.

11
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:38,000
It doesn't just complain; it fixes. Here, Gemini auto-refactors the code, applying quantization and LoRA optimizations.

12
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:48,000
Under the hood, we built a "Hybrid Grounding System." We combine deterministic AST analysis with probabilistic LLM reasoning.

13
00:01:48,500 --> 00:01:58,000
We even cross-reference predictions against the MLPerf Inference v4.1 database for ground-truth accuracy.

14
00:01:58,500 --> 00:02:08,000
The "Thinking Panel" shows you exactly how the model reasons, planning its search queries and calculations step-by-step.

15
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:18,000
With EcoCompute AI, developers can reduce their model's energy consumption by 30 to 50 percent.

16
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:28,000
Sustainable AI isn't just a goal; it's a responsibility. Join us in democratizing Green AI expertise.

17
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:35,000
EcoCompute AI. Let's Code Green.

18
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:47,000
[EcoCompute AI - Powered by Gemini 3]
